  ('cfb1883c-bf70-410d-afe2-8273467ea099', 'GENERAL', 38, '{"itemType":"CLAUSE","clause_number":"7.1","clause_title":"Provision of Bonds","clause_text":"The Contractor undertakes to obtain and deliver to the Project Manager within fourteen (14) days after the Commencement Date for approval by the Employer: (a) a Performance Bond, in the form attached to these Conditions of Contract as Appendix B (the \"Performance Bond\"), which shall be issued by a bank in the Country approved by the Employer for the purpose. Such Bond shall be in the amount stated in the Particular Conditions; and (b) an Advance Payment Bond in the form attached to these Conditions of Contract as Appendix C (the \"Advance Payment Bond\") which shall be issued by a bank in the Country approved by the Employer for the purpose. Such Bond shall be in the amount equal to the Advance Payment.","general_condition":"The Contractor undertakes to obtain and deliver to the Project Manager within fourteen (14) days after the Commencement Date for approval by the Employer: (a) a Performance Bond, in the form attached to these Conditions of Contract as Appendix B (the \"Performance Bond\"), which shall be issued by a bank in the Country approved by the Employer for the purpose. Such Bond shall be in the amount stated in the Particular Conditions; and (b) an Advance Payment Bond in the form attached to these Conditions of Contract as Appendix C (the \"Advance Payment Bond\") which shall be issued by a bank in the Country approved by the Employer for the purpose. Such Bond shall be in the amount equal to the Advance Payment.","particular_condition":"","condition_type":"General","has_time_frame":false,"time_frames":[],"comparison":[{"color":"green","comment":"General Condition from Atrium contract.","excerpt_general":"The Contractor undertakes to obtain and deliver to the Project Manager within fourteen (14) days after the Commencement Date for approval by the Employer: (a) a Performance Bond, in the form attached