  ('cfb1883c-bf70-410d-afe2-8273467ea099', 'GENERAL', 77, '{"itemType":"CLAUSE","clause_number":"11.4","clause_title":"Cost of Testing","clause_text":"The Cost of making any test shall be borne by the Contractor. The Contractor shall provide or procure the provision of all documents and other information necessary for testing and such suitably qualified and experienced staff, assistance, instruments, apparatus, machines, labour, materials, fuel, stores, samples, utilities and consumables as are necessary to carry out such tests efficiently.","general_condition":"The Cost of making any test shall be borne by the Contractor. The Contractor shall provide or procure the provision of all documents and other information necessary for testing and such suitably qualified and experienced staff, assistance, instruments, apparatus, machines, labour, materials, fuel, stores, samples, utilities and consumables as are necessary to carry out such tests efficiently.","particular_condition":"","condition_type":"General","has_time_frame":false,"time_frames":[],"comparison":[{"color":"green","comment":"General Condition from Atrium contract.","excerpt_general":"The Cost of making any test shall be borne by the Contractor. The Contractor shall provide or procure the provision of all documents and other information necessary for testing and such suitably quali...","excerpt_particular":"","type":"NO_CHANGE"}],"orderIndex":77}'::jsonb),
  ('cfb1883c-bf70-410d-afe2-8273467ea099', 'GENERAL', 78, '{"itemType":"CLAUSE","clause_number":"11.5","clause_title":"Dates for Testing","clause_text":"The Contractor shall give to the Project Manager (with a copy to the Supervision Consultant) not less than fourteen (14) days'' prior written notice of its readiness to carry out any test and shall agree with the Project Manager and the Supervision Consultant the date, time and place at which the same is to be carried out. The Contractor shall carry out such test on the date and at the time and place agreed. If the Contractor fails to carry out any such test on the date and at the time and place so agreed, any additional Costs consequently incurred by the Employer as determined by the Project Manager may be deducted by the Employer from any monies due or which may become due to the Contractor or the Employer may recover the same from the Contractor as a debt due from the Contractor. After carrying out any test the Contractor shall forthwith forward to the Project Manager (with a copy to the Supervision Consultant) a duly certified report of the test results. The provisions of this Clause 11.5 shall not apply to Tests on Completion, to which the provisions of Clause 19A.1 (Time for Tests) shall apply.","general_condition":"The Contractor shall give to the Project Manager (with a copy to the Supervision Consultant) not less than fourteen (14) days'' prior written notice of its readiness to carry out any test and shall agree with the Project Manager and the Supervision Consultant the date, time and place at which the same is to be carried out. The Contractor shall carry out such test on the date and at the time and place agreed. If the Contractor fails to carry out any such test on the date and at the time and place so agreed, any additional Costs consequently incurred by the Employer as determined by the Project Manager may be deducted by the Employer from any monies due or which may become due to the Contractor or the Employer may recover the same from the Contractor as a debt due from the Contractor. After carrying out any test the Contractor shall forthwith forward to the Project Manager (with a copy to the Supervision Consultant) a duly certified report of the test results. The provisions of this Clause 11.5 shall not apply to Tests on Completion, to which the provisions of Clause 19A.1 (Time for Tests) shall apply.","particular_condition":"","condition_type":"General","has_time_frame":false,"time_frames":[],"comparison":[{"color":"green","comment":"General Condition from Atrium contract.","excerpt_general":"The Contractor shall give to the Project Manager (with a copy to the Supervision Consultant) not less than fourteen (14) days'' prior written notice of its readiness to carry out any test and shall agr...","excerpt_particular":"","type":"NO_CHANGE"}],"orderIndex":78}'::jsonb),
  ('cfb1883c-bf70-410d-afe2-8273467ea099', 'GENERAL', 79, '{"itemType":"CLAUSE","clause_number":"11.6","clause_title":"Test Certificates","clause_text":"As and when any Plant shall have passed any particular test the Supervision Consultant shall if so requested by the Contractor sign (jointly with the Contractor) a certificate in writing furnished by the Contractor to that effect.","general_condition":"As and when any Plant shall have passed any particular test the Supervision Consultant shall if so requested by the Contractor sign (jointly with the Contractor) a certificate in writing furnished by the Contractor to that effect.","particular_condition":"","condition_type":"General","has_time_frame":false,"time_frames":[],"comparison":[{"color":"green","comment":"General Condition from Atrium contract.","excerpt_general":"As and when any Plant shall have passed any particular test the Supervision Consultant shall if so requested by the Contractor sign (jointly with the Contractor) a certificate in writing furnished by ...","excerpt_particular":"","type":"NO_CHANGE"}],"orderIndex":79}'::jsonb),
  ('cfb1883c-bf70-410d-afe2-8273467ea099', 'GENERAL', 80, '{"itemType":"CLAUSE","clause_number":"11.7","clause_title":"Rejection and Remedy","clause_text":"If at any time the Supervision Consultant shall as a result of any inspection, examination, measurement and/or test decide that any workmanship and/or Plant (including materials for the manufacture or fabrication thereof and/or samples of such materials) is defective or otherwise not in accordance with the Contract he shall, notwithstanding any earlier inspection, examination, measurement and/or test or any interim payment, have power to order the Contractor in writing to: (a) make good the defect or otherwise take such steps as may be necessary to ensure that the workmanship or Plant complies with the Contract; and/or (b) remove from the Site, within such time as may be specified in the order, any Plant which in his opinion is defective or otherwise not in accordance with the Contract and substitute proper and suitable Plant; and the Contractor shall comply with any such order in a timely manner and at its sole Cost. Thereafter the Supervision Consultant may require any relevant testing to be repeated and may stipulate a reasonable period, having regard to the requirements of the Programme, within which such repeated testing must be carried out and completed. The Cost of.....................","general_condition":"If at any time the Supervision Consultant shall as a result of any inspection, examination, measurement and/or test decide that any workmanship and/or Plant (including materials for the manufacture or fabrication thereof and/or samples of such materials) is defective or otherwise not in accordance with the Contract he shall, notwithstanding any earlier inspection, examination, measurement and/or test or any interim payment, have power to order the Contractor in writing to: (a) make good the defect or otherwise take such steps as may be necessary to ensure that the workmanship or Plant complies with the 